Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:38.91,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I'm Kunimi Hiro, a first year pitcher with Senkawa High School's baseball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.75,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I'm a close friend of Tachibana Hideo, the cleanup hitter for Meiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:49.06,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,He asked me to pinch-hit on \Nhis date, and I couldn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.10,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,The date is with Hikari,\N my childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:56.55,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I've known her\Nsince we were little...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.16,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,...so there shouldn't be any reason for me to feel nervous, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:19.34,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HEFA7A6&\3c&H33322D&\move(615,119,29,116,6,7305)}Nontenora{" [note: Cinderella ?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:32.65,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H4546BE&\fscx88\fscy87\pos(430,276)}Red Broncross
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.24,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.40,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.02,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.02,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, you weren't on the train ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.36,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Nope.\N I figured this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.00,def2,.HIKARI..,0,0,0,,You've always done things\Nlike this since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.40,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.31,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.96,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,This flavor brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:38.82,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:42.15,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,We haven't gone out together in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.47,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Really ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.27,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.40,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.05,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.84,def2,OLDWOMAN:,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:16.79,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.84,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What is it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.02,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.65,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What is it ? It bugs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.73,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,It bothers you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.55,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:38.04,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I just thought, "Until recently, you\Ncouldn't even reach the strap handle."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.90,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.10,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:46.19,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I have big hands and feet,\Nso I'll definitely grow bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.32,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You've certainly grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.14,def2,OLDWOMAN:,0,0,0,,Here, please have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:15.95,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:42.10,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,When I'm needed by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:48.95,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG:..,0,0,0,,...I learn for the first time where I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:56.60,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Just as the metronome gets interrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:04.56,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,...so few people can hear the monotonous sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:12.48,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,With a clunk, I place my forehead on the display window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:22.03,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,For what can I cry ? I look up beyond the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:29.84,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,When you're not with me, you overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:38.03,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,On the streets and by the windows, the clues overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:46.31,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Loneliness doesn't corner us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:54.53,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Rather, it teaches us whom we cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:20.10,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Even those long, difficult nights that make us retreat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:30.38,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,...we'll be able to laugh about someday, like a childhood scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:41.90,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Let's return to "two of us," let's return together...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:50.17,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,...rather than losing our time to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:58.30,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Happiness is not something that someone does for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:06.95,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,It means that I have someone I can embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.04,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.06,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:53.10,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Was the can of juice{from the train platform} tasty ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.35,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.26,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You know him ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.27,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.00,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I got to know him \Nabout three hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.45,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HDEDEE5&\pos(357,86)\frz8.208}Shin-Tokoroguchiko Station
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:16.15,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HCDCCBC&\a5\fscx86\fscy82\pos(367,374)}Service suspended between\NShirai and Mikami,\Ndue to flooding on the tracks. \NThank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.70,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Man, it was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.56,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Because of the sudden rainstorm, the concert was cut short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:26.80,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Girls' underwear was showing through, and train service is stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.70,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Really, we've got to have more \Noutdoor concerts during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.30,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:31.90,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.00,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,It's 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.65,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Do you think this is that \Nwell-known course of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:48.19,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,...where the couple who can't go\Nhome and spend the night together ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.30,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:54.60,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,In half an hour or so, they say that train service will resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.90,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.35,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Let's go spend some time\Nat the café near the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.10,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Run !
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:37.60,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What kind of things do you \Nusually talk about with Hideo ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:38.60,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You want to know ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:40.79,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.85,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.23,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,About social service, environmental issues...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.00,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,...taxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.80,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,And about our dreams{hopes}\Nfor the future, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.84,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Dreams ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.45,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What's Hideo's dream for the future ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.17,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,First, the Koushien.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.09,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Then professional ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.05,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Rookie of the Year. \NAll-Star appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.30,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Individual titles.\NThe team winning the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:13.31,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Breaking several records, and retiring afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:16.04,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Become a commentator \Nand then a field manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:19.70,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,And three children in\Na heartwarming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.30,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,And you're the wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.01,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,He didn't say that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.03,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,There's no need to even hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.19,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,You want to become a pro, too ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.22,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:39.09,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Playing baseball for\Na living sounds tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.10,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure I'll play baseball until I can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:47.12,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,But it can be bush-league or anything, in my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.06,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:14:00.32,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I always want you to\Nplay baseball for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.94,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,So ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.00,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Hm ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.20,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What's your dream ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:12.60,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,The perfect crime and political reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.90,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, the rain seems to have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.40,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I do want to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:33.65,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,But before that, I want to find a \Njob where I can feel confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:39.65,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,And become an independent adult who has her own perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.53,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,So you want to become a\N"career-focused woman" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:46.25,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I don't mean something grand like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:50.87,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,But at least, I don't want to live \Nmy life just following my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:01.22,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,So I don't really mind if my husband is a professional baseball player...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.30,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,...or an ace pitcher for the\Nneighborhood baseball league...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.30,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.58,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "oops" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:14.12,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Well, the trains seem\Nto be running. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.61,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.70,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,What are you doing ? We'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.80,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.90,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we avoided trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.35,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,What do you mean ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:43.32,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,If we couldn't go home and had to spend\Nthe night together, Hideo would beat me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:45.77,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Why ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.95,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Why ? It's a given !
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.17,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,A man and a woman\Nspending the night together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.43,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,{laughs} What could possibly happen between you and me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:16:00.30,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, you sound confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.70,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,It's a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.55,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,It's strange.\NI wonder where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.00,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.05,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,There's no ring here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.65,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,You shouldn't make\Nsuch a hasty conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.20,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.91,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,Really, I wonder where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:40.23,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Shall we give up ? Okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.02,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,No ! Look for it !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:43.14,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.60,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,That's right.\N It's an engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.65,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right, Miss !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.31,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Hikari, right ?\NYou're definitely right !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:57.21,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,You must be happy to \Nhave such a great girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:59.00,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm such a bad girlfriend !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.25,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:04.50,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,I mean, it's your fault, Lacchie !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.00,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,It's your fault for proposing to me in a place like this !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:10.90,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,I wanted to put it on your finger after the concert !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:15.55,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, you shouldn't fight, Lacchie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.10,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,That's right. You'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.00,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.44,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Can it be found...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:23.55,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,We will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.00,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,It's here !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.01,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,Really ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.20,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Thank goodness !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.43,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.25,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:54.00,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Right now, it's still a glass ring, but someday, I'll give you the real ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:58.90,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,A shiny one. So have faith in me, and stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.29,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I guess they're shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.72,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's shiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.05,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:22.85,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:23.65,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.90,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hurry up, or we'll\Nbe late for the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.03,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.95,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,By the time we get home, it'll be midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.17,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.80,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Leave them alone !\NWe don't have time !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.93,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:15.75,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.28,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Hikari !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.30,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,Darling, I can't hold it anymore !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:34.44,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,The baby's coming out !\N He's coming out !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.41,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Are you okay ? Hang in there !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.66,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,We're definitely not helping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.17,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,Darling, I can't hold it anymore !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:48.60,def2,..MAN:...,0,0,0,,Hang in there ! I'll take you to the hospital right way !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:57.97,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Dammit !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.40,def2,.WOMAN:..,0,0,0,,The baby's coming out...!
