Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:37.10,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:52.36,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I'm glad that couple made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:53.34,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Yeah.
