Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:45.83,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(311.111,468.444)}The star I'm watching today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:50.31,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.556,464.889)}...glistened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:55.93,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,467.556)}In the town full of things that disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:23:00.06,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.667,465.778)}...I thought to myself, wishfully:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:08.01,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.667,467.556)}Let's return to "two of us," let's return together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:16.16,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.556,469.333)}...rather than losing our time to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:19.56,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,464.889)}Happiness is not something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:24.39,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(313.778,466.667)}...that someone does for me.
