Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.89,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Oh well, in the end, \Nwe couldn't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:46.54,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,But I feel safe with Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:47.93,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:50.21,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,I mean, we're like siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:55.01,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,You don't understand. You're an attractive woman who makes men's hearts throb.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:56.46,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Is that what you say ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.27,def2,.KUNIMI:.,0,0,0,,Well, I might, or might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:00.65,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, Hiro is going to turn into a wolf !
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:06.67,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Next episode of H2 is, "I Can't Sleep... A Night With Just the Two of Us."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:07.73,def2,.HIKARI:.,0,0,0,,Are you having a refreshing workout ?
